        "product_description": {
            "value": "ParaLace 550 Paracord Shoelaces are built for adventure and designed to withstand even the most rugged outdoor environments. Made from durable 550 paracord and sold in pairs, these round hiking boot laces resist abrasion, weather, wear and tear, and UV deterioration. With a 550lb static load strength and low-stretch nylon construction, they outperform regular laces—keeping knots secure for fewer adjustments and more comfortable movement. Their kernmantle design features 9 removable inner nylon strands enclosed by a woven nylon sheath and capped with 4mm black metal aglets that prevent fraying. Compatible with most hiking boots, running shoes, work boots, combat boots, and more, they also double as versatile survival gear: build a snare, make a sling, extract fishing line, hang a hammock, or secure a shelter. Available in 48, 54, 60, 72, and 81 inch lengths, these unisex Od Green laces are an easy, lightweight addition to your outdoor gear.",
            "is_required": true,
            "source": "ai",
            "model": "claude-opus-4-8"
        },
